trans-unit.source: Provides standard facilities for creating and managing a type-safe, ordered collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableRowGroup"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Brukes til standard for å opprette og administrere en type sikker, i samling <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.TableRowGroup"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This collection supports standard zero-based indexing.
trans-unit.target: Denne samlingen støtter standard nullbasert indeksering.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Table.RowGroups%2A> property provided by the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Table> class returns a TableRowGroupCollection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Table.RowGroups%2A>egenskapen som er angitt av den <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Table>klassen returnerer en TableRowGroupCollection.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.Table> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Table.RowGroups%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [How to: Manipulate a Table's Row Groups through the RowGroups Property](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [slik: endre en tabell radgrupper via egenskapen RowGroups](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The Capacity property represents the number of pre-allocated slots for storing items in this collection, whereas the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRowGroupCollection.Count%2A> property represents the actual number of items currently in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen kapasitet representerer hvor mange diskblokker spor for lagring av elementer i denne samlingen mens den <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRowGroupCollection.Count%2A>egenskapen representerer faktisk antall elementer i samlingen.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRowGroupCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: The value of Capacity is always at least as large as the value of <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRowGroupCollection.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for kapasitet er alltid minst stor som verdien for <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRowGroupCollection.Count%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.TableRowGroupCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: When newly added collection items cause the collection count to exceed the collection capacity, the capacity is automatically increased to accommodate the newly added collection items.
trans-unit.target: Når nye Samlingselementer føre til at samlinger vil overskride samlingen kapasitet, kapasiteten økes automatisk å gi plass til nye Samlingselementer.

trans-unit.source: Increasing the collection capacity involves allocating additional collection slots, which incurs both performance and memory overhead.
trans-unit.target: Øke samlingen kapasiteten innebærer tildeling av flere samlingen spor, som medfører både ytelse og minneforbruk.
